<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<entry xmlns:functx="http://www.functx.com" xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="entry_īwmæ"
    xml:lang="os">
    <form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma">
        <orth>īwmæ</orth>
    </form>
    <form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal">
        <orth>ewmæ</orth>
    </form>
    <sense>
        <cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
            <q>вместе</q>
        </cit>
        <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <q>together</q>
        </cit>
    </sense>
    <cit type="exampleGroup">
        <cit type="example">
            <quote>īwmæ næ rambyrd kæn</quote>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                <q>собери нас вместе</q>
            </cit>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <q>get us together</q>
            </cit>
            <bibl>
                <ref target="#src_Коста"/>
                <biblScope>39</biblScope>
            </bibl>
        </cit>
        <cit type="example">
            <quote>īwmæjag</quote>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                <q>общий</q>
            </cit>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <q>mutual</q>
            </cit>
        </cit>
    </cit>
    <cit type="exampleGroup">
        <cit type="example">
            <quote>īwmæ næ rambyrd kæn</quote>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                <q>собери нас вместе</q>
            </cit>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <q>get us together</q>
            </cit>
            <bibl>
                <ref target="#src_Коста"/>
                <biblScope>39</biblScope>
            </bibl>
        </cit>
        <cit type="example">
            <quote>īwmæjag</quote>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                <q>общий</q>
            </cit>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <q>mutual</q>
            </cit>
        </cit>
    </cit>
    <etym xml:lang="ru">Направительный падеж от <ref type="xr" target="#entry_īw"/> | %iew%i ‘один’,
        лексикализовавшийся в наречном значении. Точно такое же образование в
            %bгрузинском:%b<mentioned xml:lang="ka"
            ><lang/><w>ertad</w><gloss><q>вместе</q></gloss></mentioned> — направительный падеж от
        %ierti%i ‘один’. Употребляясь послеложно, %iīwmæ%i стало падежным формантом совместного
        падежа: %i-imæ%i из %iīwmæ%i (<bibl><ref target="#ref_ОЯФ_I"
            /><biblScope>101</biblScope></bibl>).</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">An allative case from <ref type="xr" target="#entry_īw"/> | %iew%i ‘one’,
        lexicalized in the adverbial meaning. The same formation is attested in <mentioned
            xml:lang="ka"><lang/><w>ertad</w><gloss><q>together</q></gloss></mentioned> — it is an
        allative case from %ierti%i ‘one’. Being used as a postposition, %iīwmæ%i became a case
        marker of comitative case: %i-imæ%i from %iīwmæ%i (<bibl><ref target="#ref_ОЯФ_I"
                /><biblScope>101</biblScope></bibl>).</etym>
</entry>
